channel.title: DeltaScape help needed
channel.description:
I'm using a DeltaScape source, and i've fixed most anti-leech.
Theres one, though, that i'm finding quite hard to fix.
Now I know alot of you will be big headed and say that I shouldn't use DeltaScape if I cannot fix this anti-leech. But please, just tell me how to fix it, i'll be very grateful and i'll rep++.
It's the anti-leech in which causes you to die constantly, and spawn bones as you walk.
Thanks alot, - RuneX -
